WEBVTT

00:00:00.421 --> 00:00:02.595
Track 09.06

00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:05.423
Narrator: 1

00:00:05.924 --> 00:00:07.987
A: Can you go to the shops?

00:00:08.078 --> 00:00:09.440
We need bread.

00:00:09.771 --> 00:00:12.548
B: Sorry, I’m really busy.

00:00:12.788 --> 00:00:15.473
A: Oh, OK, I’ll do it then.

00:00:17.254 --> 00:00:18.279
Narrator: 2

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:21.533
A: Can you do something for me?

00:00:21.752 --> 00:00:23.458
B: Sure, what is it?

00:00:23.769 --> 00:00:26.454
A: Could you meet me at the station on Sunday?

00:00:26.626 --> 00:00:28.318
B: Yes, certainly.

00:00:28.372 --> 00:00:31.269
A: Thanks, that’s really kind of you.

00:00:33.378 --> 00:00:34.383
Narrator: 3

00:00:35.518 --> 00:00:37.857
A: Can you come to the shops with me today?

00:00:38.226 --> 00:00:41.195
B: Sorry, I can’t. I’m really busy.

00:00:41.874 --> 00:00:43.345
A: Oh, OK.

00:00:43.959 --> 00:00:45.610
Could you come with me tomorrow?

00:00:45.841 --> 00:00:47.550
B: Sure, no problem.

00:00:47.728 --> 00:00:48.558
A: Thanks.